502
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:17,960
Apa kau kehilangan banyak orang, John?

503
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:20,600
<i>Tapi kau jarang membicarakan tentang mereka.</i>

504
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:25,770
Menurutmu kenapa?

505
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:30,710
Resiko pekerjaan.

506
00:23:30,710 --> 00:23:36,350
