520
00:24:23,430 --> 00:24:26,090
<i>Sekarang Caroline ingin anda bicara dengan lantang,</i>

521
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:28,300
<i>karena suaranya sudah dibungkam.</i>

522
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:29,930
<i>Bagaimana kabar Emma?</i>

523
00:24:29,930 --> 00:24:31,100
Dia terlihat sedikit khawatir

524
00:24:31,100 --> 00:24:32,300
