526
00:24:33,700 --> 00:24:35,140
<i>Sudah menemukan si Fixer?</i>

527
00:24:35,140 --> 00:24:36,870
<i>jadi kita bisa menghentikan semua ini</i>

528
00:24:36,870 --> 00:24:39,610
