00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:46,670
<i>menunjukan Chad Bryson sedang bertengkar</i>

657
00:29:46,670 --> 00:29:48,270
<i>dengan istrinya, Caroline Mills,</i>

658
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:50,370
